
;アイテム説明と購入数
;ARG→選択項目
@ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_DETAIL(ARG)

;対応IDでないなら汎用出して帰る
;ここでは選択項目による
IF ARG < 10 || ARG > 10 +ESTATE_LIST_NUM
	PRINTL  　《 Item Description Shown Here 》
	RETURN
ENDIF

SELECTCASE ARG
CASE 10
    PRINTFORM New Cowshed Construction  Number Built: {ITEM:牛舎} Units
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:牛舎)
    PRINTL
    PRINTL Constructs a cowshed for managing slaves with 【Lactating】 status collectively.
    PRINTL An initial cowshed has a capacity for 10 slaves, and up to 10 cowsheds can be built.

CASE 11
    PRINTFORM Cowshed Expansion  Number Built: {ITEM:牛舎} Units
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ESTATE_COWSHED_EXTENSION)
    PRINTL
    PRINTL Selects a built cowshed to expand, increasing the number of slaves it can house.
    PRINTL Each expansion adds room for 10 slaves, up to a maximum capacity of 100 slaves.

CASE 12
    PRINTFORM Office Expansion  Current Expansions: {ITEM:事務所増築} Times
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:事務所増築)
    PRINTL
    PRINTL Expands the ranch office, adding four additional rooms for slave allocation.
    PRINTL Assigned slaves are treated as employees, slightly increasing living costs but enhancing
    PRINTL stamina recovery during breaks and sleep.

CASE 13
    PRINTFORM Remodel to Family Bath
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:家族風呂)
    PRINTL Requires 【Office Expansion】 at least once
    PRINTL
    PRINTFORML Enlarges the ranch bath, allowing you and the slaves to bathe together.
    PRINTL Bathing together restores slave stamina.
    PRINTL Enables skinship interactions while in the bath.
    PRINTL
    PRINTL This bath is likely intended for family use rather than for erotic activities.

CASE 14
    PRINTFORM Large Bathhouse Construction
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:大浴場)
    PRINTL Requires <Family Bath>
    PRINTL
    PRINTL Constructs a large bathhouse where slaves can bathe together.
    PRINTL Adds <Large Bathhouse Cleaning> to the schedule, removing the one-person limit.
    PRINTL With a 【Large Bathhouse Cleaning Completion】 of 100%, the bathhouse can be used that day.
    PRINTL
    PRINTL (Heavy labor required; high stamina and cleaning skills in slaves are recommended.)

CASE 15
    PRINTFORM Additional Pet House  Current Houses: {ITEM:ペット小屋} Units
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:ペット小屋)
    PRINTL Requires 【Office Expansion】 at least once
    PRINTL
    PRINTL Constructs an additional house for keeping large pets.
    PRINTL Required for acquiring [Fallen Horse], [Orthros], and [Demon Realm Hamster].

CASE 16
    PRINTFORM Slave Dormitory Construction
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:奴隷寮)
    PRINTL Requires 【Office Expansion】 at least once
    PRINTL
    PRINTL Builds a <Slave Dormitory> for slaves, allowing them to live and work as employees.
    PRINTL Two rooms are provided initially, each accommodating four slaves.

CASE 17
    PRINTFORM Slave Dormitory Expansion  Current Expansions: {ITEM:奴隷寮増築} Times
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:奴隷寮増築)
    PRINTL Requires <Slave Dormitory>
    PRINTL
    PRINTL Expands the <Slave Dormitory> by adding one more room.

CASE 18
    PRINTFORM Remodel to System Kitchen
    CALL ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ITEMPRICE:システムキッチン)
    PRINTL Requires 【Office Expansion】 at least once
    PRINTL
    PRINTFORML Allows you or slaves to prepare a meal for all employees at once.
    PRINTL Costs slightly more than individual meals, but has stamina recovery benefits.
    PRINTL The higher the character's 【Cooking】 level, the better the recovery and the wider the menu options.
    PRINTL
    PRINTFORML If the cook has the 【Lactating】 trait, meals can be made with %SAVESTR:表記／母乳% upon request,
    PRINTFORML and you can assist with milking if needed.

ENDSELECT



;費用表示：前の名残でとりあえず関数化
;ARG→費用
@ITEM_SHOP_ESTATE_PRICE(ARG)

PRINTFORML 　費用：%VALUE_DIGIT(ARG)%G





